<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🎁 Just4You · Creatief Cadeau</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdf5e6 0%, #f7e8d4 100%);
            font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .kaart {
            max-width: 550px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
            border-radius: 60px 30px 60px 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 45px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(200, 170, 130, 0.3);
        }

        .creativiteit {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2c241a;
        }

        .creativiteit span {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #c69c6d, #a57248);
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .sterretje {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #dbb88c;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .boodschap {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #5c4a34;
            border-top: 1px solid #ecdbba;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ecdbba;
            padding: 18px 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }

        .contact-blok {
            background: #fef7ef;
            border-radius: 35px;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .icoon {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            min-width: 45px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .link {
            color: #9b6e42;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0c8b0;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        .link:hover {
            color: #7a5434;
            border-bottom-color: #c49a6c;
        }

        .knop {
            background: #e8d9cc;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 40px;
            padding: 5px 14px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: monospace;
            transition: 0.1s;
        }

        .knop:active {
            background: #d4c2b2;
        }

        .quote {
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #bc9a77;
            font-family: monospace;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .kaart {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            .creativiteit {
                font-size: 1.7rem;
            }
            .item {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            .icoon {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
                min-width: 35px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="kaart">
    <div class="creativiteit">
        een cadeau vol <span>creativiteit</span>…
    </div>
    <div class="sterretje">✦ ✦ ✦</div>

    <div class="boodschap">
        Ieder geschenk is een verhaal.<br>
        Vertel het jouwe met een unieke, persoonlijke ervaring.
    </div>

    <div class="contact-blok">
        <div class="item">
            <div class="icoon">📧</div>
            <div>
                <a href="mailto:just4you@proximus.be" class="link">just4you@proximus.be</a>
                <button class="knop" data-kopie="just4you@proximus.be">📋 kopieer</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <div class="icoon">📞</div>
            <div>
                <a href="tel:+32478911165" class="link">0478 91 11 65</a>
                <button class="knop" data-kopie="0478 91 11 65">📋 kopieer</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="quote">
        ✨ Meer info of vragen? Ik luister graag. ✨
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.knop').forEach(knop => {
        knop.addEventListener('click', function() {
            const tekst = this.getAttribute('data-kopie');
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(tekst).then(() => {
                const origineel = this.innerHTML;
                this.innerHTML = '✓ gekopieerd!';
                setTimeout(() => {
                    this.innerHTML = origineel;
                }, 1500);
            });
        });
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>
